{"tid":967432,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖，極醜惡！) 某間將軍澳炸雞店","createTime":"2019-01-03T13:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T10:06:37.000Z","uid":217344,"like":2357,"dislike":114,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"3e13e8adb6e96da4897a395f474620236461a72e","tid":967432,"uid":217344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟有一日同女朋友去咗呢間韓國炸雞，嗌咗碟韓式BBQ烤雞拼原味烤雞 ( half &amp; half)。誰不知嚟到嘅時候兩個雞髀係咁。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KqVJh9p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKqVJh9p.png&h=4a93c8c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJ7GPgb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJ7GPgb.png&h=b5e5c3d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qhwo2Bj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhwo2Bj.png&h=8860506c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oo5QHBs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOo5QHBs.png&h=7ce149fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有乜理由啲雞脾一上就係見到骨，好似俾人食過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？我質問個侍應佢就話冇攞走過啲肉，係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過咗幾日我仲係好唔憤氣，以我由細食雞脾食到大嘅經驗唔應該係咁！所以過咗幾日之後去咗kfc 嗌個餐來睇。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NEZepQ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNEZepQ2.png&h=a1e430b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VpSLwv5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVpSLwv5.png&h=80a83a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然係炸得好樣衰但係都起碼完整嘅一舊，究竟係我食得雞少定間餐廳有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街係餐廳偷工減料，開佢名<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓豬見識少，識食一定係咁食"},{"pid":"0d839c4aa1acbc76e0ce1c275098aad9fd5e609c","tid":967432,"uid":220180,"like":141,"dislike":1,"score":140,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"樓主開名屌柒佢啦"},{"pid":"b4fe9a40b74f925f48bd5a367b137d933433e3ec","tid":967432,"uid":53374,"like":431,"dislike":2,"score":429,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:18:49.000Z","msg":"goobne chicken?"},{"pid":"ba261ac691543294b75a0a8436be46492d3b315a","tid":967432,"uid":49226,"like":19,"dislike":595,"score":-576,"quote":{"pid":"0d839c4aa1acbc76e0ce1c275098aad9fd5e609c","tid":967432,"uid":220180,"like":141,"dislike":1,"score":140,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"樓主開名屌柒佢啦"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:23:13.000Z","msg":"Kfc 都要開名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a380cee71660269bca3209a1eb0c401b9dfa35cc","tid":967432,"uid":65024,"like":403,"dislike":3,"score":400,"quote":{"pid":"b4fe9a40b74f925f48bd5a367b137d933433e3ec","tid":967432,"uid":53374,"like":431,"dislike":2,"score":429,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:18:49.000Z","msg":"goobne chicken?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"呢間野聽執都得，長期無客"},{"pid":"b9d8b893fced1a8a480025d8742c8db3bb9b2481","tid":967432,"uid":178800,"like":467,"dislike":2,"score":465,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"一定係斬哂d肉搭其他菜色啦<br />\n例如泡菜炒飯，雞絲冷麵之類<br />\n慳到咁，正垃圾"},{"pid":"4f406f15b6e7227e794dbbc47a673555e4205c5c","tid":967432,"uid":123053,"like":167,"dislike":2,"score":165,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"真係俾狗食<br />\n得條骨"},{"pid":"11aa615f0f6968a504b39cae1bd91689c1e4ecf2","tid":967432,"uid":127611,"like":241,"dislike":3,"score":238,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"唔開名死全家<br />\n開名就餐廳老闆死全家"},{"pid":"1956ff76d4d0ca27cc1617c4c2734d5107a3e395","tid":967432,"uid":84